name: Country Playing Field
description:
This piece was minted as part of the #HENpocalypse and #HEN200 events. The photograph is part of a larger set from this day as a kind of 'study on...' the place. I've not seen football played here, but we flew my kite once or twice the Christmas I got it at my grandparents. They used to do stock car racing here, or about here too, the videos of which are good fun.

|  3550x1997px | f/4, 1/250s, 50mm | Canon 400D and Lightroom | Photographed 13th August, 2018, Peasenhall, Sibton, Suffolk |
